PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Sui Transaction Analysis App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is the Sui Transaction Analysis App?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides real-time monitoring and analysis of new transactions on the Sui blockchain. It allows you to explore transaction details, track assets, and gain insights into on-chain activity.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: The app connects to Sui nodes and listens for new block confirmations. When a new block is mined, it parses the transactions and extracts relevant data like sender, receiver, asset types, amounts, and metadata.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of analysis can I perform?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You can view transaction histories, track asset movements, analyze trends and patterns, and set up alerts for specific transaction types or addresses of interest.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app suitable for businesses?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app is designed for both individual and enterprise use cases. Businesses can leverage the data to monitor their on-chain operations, analyze user behavior, and make informed decisions.
